HEADWORD: Diaphanoscope
<hw>Di`a*phan"o*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
transparent + <ets>-scope</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Photog.)</fld> <def>A dark
